Sentencas: The La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta (LSM)-coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) cathode with 3D core-shell architecture has been fabricated by the solution impregnation technology.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: On the basis of previous research, the synthetic process is improved in order to promote the perovskite degree of BSCF.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In this paper, the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) mechanism of LSM-coated BSCF is studied in detail.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: As the intervention of LSM shell, the LSM-coated BSCF presents the different ORR rate-determining step comparing with the BSCF cathode.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The formation and transfer of lattice oxygen in LSM is the rate-determining step for the LSM-coated BSCF cathode, while the molecular oxygen surface adsorption for the BSCF cathode.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In the single cells test, the LSM-coated BSCF cell shows a higher maximum power density than the uncoated cell.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The remarkable CO2-poisoning resistant performance of LSM-coated BSCF is verified by the CO2-TPD test and the single cell potentiostatic test.
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The excellent electrochemical performance and CO2-poisoning resistance indicate that LSM-coated BSCF cathode appears to be a promising cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Study on the ORR Mechanism and CO2-Poisoning Resistance of La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ-Coated Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
